item.title: CVE-2017-17163|2024-08-05T20:43:59.901Z -- huawei%20technologies%20co.%2C%20ltd. -- secospace%20usg6600
item.description: Huawei Secospace USG6600 V500R001C30SPC100 has an Out-of-Bounds memory access vulnerability due to insufficient verification. An authenticated local attacker can make processing crash by executing some commands. The attacker can exploit this vulnerability to cause a denial of service.
